Christopher Theron Usher

Age : 56Public asset : 83,481 USDLinked companies :  Ion Geophysical Corp 





Summary 



Mr. Christopher T. Usher is EVP & Chief Innovation Officer-Innovation Division at ION Geophysical Corp., a Member at Society of Exploration Geophysicists, and a Member at European Association of Geoscientists & Engineers.Mr. Usher was previously employed as CTO, Senior VP-Data Processing & Analysis by Global Geophysical Services, Inc., Senior Director-Landmark Software & Services by Halliburton Co., Senior Vice President-Integrated Services by Paradigm BV, President-Global Data Processing Division by Petroleum Geo-Services, Inc., and Vice President-Worldwide Technology by Western Geophysical Co.He also served on the board at Sensilaser Technologies, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from Yale University.



