Sensilaser Technologies, Inc.

                    Sensilaser Technologies, Inc. provides fibre optic sensing technology services. It produces precision, low noise lasers. Sensilaser lasers are built for sensing and measurement systems where precision and reliability are critical for success. Its field studies have proven its potential in creating sustainable energy solutions in both offshore oil and gas and wind energy generation. The company was founded by David Cox and He Qing in 2005 and is headquartered in Montreal, Canada.                  





